{"tid":1034446,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"將軍澳善明邨母子自殺　子死母送院","createTime":"2019-02-24T02:19:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-24T02:21:06.000Z","uid":41404,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7f926a5ec273f1a73538f0df837cf292004cb43a","tid":1034446,"uid":41404,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T02:19:19.000Z","msg":"昨晚(23日)10時29分，將軍澳善明邨善禮樓，保安員報案指一對母子反鎖在單位內，消防到場破門入屋，赫見一名年約20歲男子當場死亡，其50餘歲母親仍然清醒，由救護車送院搶救。警方將現場封鎖調查，案件暫列作企圖自殺，交由刑事調查隊跟進。<br />\n<br />\n今晨(24日)8時許，死者遺體由仵工舁送殮房，等候剖驗以確定死因，探員在單位內檢走多袋證物，包括棉被等。<br />\n<br />\n防止自殺求助熱線：<br />\n<br />\n香港撒瑪利亞防止自殺會： 2389 2222<br />\n生命熱線： 2382 0000<br />\n明愛向晴軒： 18288<br />\n<br />\n社會福利署： 2343 2255<br />\n撒瑪利亞會熱線(多種語言)： 2896 0000<br />\n東華三院芷若園： 18281<br />\n<br />\n醫管局精神健康專線： 2466 7350<br />\n利民會： 3512 2626<br />\n賽馬會青少年情緒健康網上支援平台「Open噏」：<a href=\"http://www.openup.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.openup.hk&d=5l33Zop1uuimQiJtW1o9xQb0NiVgWGuYP6yHf6H5SmE%3D&h=d8e91c8d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">www.openup.hk</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190224/mobile/bkn-20190224072251105-0224_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190224%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20190224072251105-0224_00822_001.html&d=5l33Zop1uuimQiJtW1o9xQb0NiVgWGuYP6yHf6H5SmE%3D&h=3cdabff0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190224/mobile/bkn-20190224072251105-0224_00822_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"bb9f152545d2e424ff0ed953801b84573bd72041","tid":1034446,"uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T02:21:06.000Z","msg":"雙人擦首抽"}]}